messages.message: Hi team, SocGen would like us to commit to a 12-months LTS from end of mainstream support particularly for our API. Who can help me to add this to our long-term roadmap for all our customers? Looking at the market's standard , we generally see some terms published online.
Probably @Josh Rad could take a look at this when he’s back next week? Might be a question for the legal team, I’m not very familiar with this.
